    "bodyHtml": "<objective>\nArchive phase directories from completed milestones into `.planning/milestones/v{X.Y}-phases/`.\n\n<p>Use when <code>.planning/phases/</code> has accumulated directories from past milestones.\n</objective></p>\n<execution_context>\n@vendor/get-anything-done/workflows/cleanup.md\n</execution_context>\n\n<process>\nFollow the cleanup workflow at @vendor/get-anything-done/workflows/cleanup.md.\nIdentify completed milestones, show a dry-run summary, and archive on confirmation.\n</process>\n",
    "bodyRaw": "<objective>\nArchive phase directories from completed milestones into `.planning/milestones/v{X.Y}-phases/`.\n\nUse when `.planning/phases/` has accumulated directories from past milestones.\n</objective>\n\n<execution_context>\n@vendor/get-anything-done/workflows/cleanup.md\n</execution_context>\n\n<process>\nFollow the cleanup workflow at @vendor/get-anything-done/workflows/cleanup.md.\nIdentify completed milestones, show a dry-run summary, and archive on confirmation.\n</process>\n"
